{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":4389,"name":"","username":"sabotage3d","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/sabotage3d/{size}/87_2.png","created_at":"2015-01-28T00:37:18.000Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eHi guys,\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI am getting some weird offset with convexhull. If I change in Sample 11 Physics this line:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cpre\u003e\u003ccode class=\"lang-auto\"\u003eshape-\u0026gt;SetBox(Vector3::ONE);\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003cp\u003ewith this one :\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\nshape-\u0026gt;SetConvexHull(cache-\u0026gt;GetResource\u0026lt;Model\u0026gt;(\"Models/Box.mdl\"));\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI am getting a gap when the bodies come to rest. Because of this gap it seems that friction is ignored.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThat is the hash number of the commit I am using : 401f478abfa0a5957807f0c80b4b994d7d944ff0\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"http://i.imgur.com/3B6nx1y.png\" title=\"\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3B6nx1y.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"654\" height=\"500\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#far-image\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003cspan class=\"filename\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"informations\"\u003e943√ó720\u003c/span\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cuse xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"\u003e\u003c/use\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-01-02T01:03:00.187Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":42,"reads":4,"readers_count":3,"score":212.8,"yours":false,"topic_id":800,"topic_slug":"solved-convexhull-offset","displa